                    <ab>+ In nomine domini salvatoris nostri ihesu christi dei eterni.<persName
                            key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis #childOf #grandchildOf"
                            ref="#people/3010"> secundus Riccardus</persName> divina ordinante
                        clementia Capuanorum <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs> pro redemptione anime
                        sue hoc clementer concessit et confirmavit. Notum sit fidelibus dei
                        presentibus et posteris. quod Ego secundus Riccardus gratia dei Capuanorum
                        princeps. ob salutem et remedium animarum <rs key="#Princeps">principum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps #grandparentOf" ref="#people/3001"
                            >Riccardi</persName> scilicet <rs key="#grandparentOf">avi</rs> et
                            <persName key="#Princeps #parentOf" ref="#people/3002"
                            >Iordanis</persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patris</rs> mei et ob statum principatus mei. ob Concedo
                        et confirmo. <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3000">Sancti
                            Laurentii</orgName> Levite et martiris christi sito circa <rs
                            key="#Walls">muros</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #Walls" ref="#places/4000">aversane</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Cities">urbis</rs>. et dompno <persName
                            key="#Abbots #Personal_rank" ref="#people/3016">Guarino</persName>
                        eiusdem monasterii <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabili</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">Abbati</rs> suisque successoribus in perpetuum. videlicet.
                            <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3006">Sancti Laurentii</orgName> constructum in
                        capua cum universis rebus et pertinentiis qualiter modo possidet et
                        dominatur et qualiter sibi quoquo legali modo pertinere videtur. et <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3011">Sancte Reparate. </orgName> et <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3029">Sancti blasii</orgName> cum omnibus
                        pertinentiis suis. et unum <rs key="#Mills">molendinum</rs> quod est in
                            <placeName key="#Rivers #Shores #Ports" ref="#places/609"
                            >vulturni</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Rivers">flumine</rs>. et <persName><name ref="Huuarnari"
                                >Guannerius</name></persName> dedit et obtulit prescripto monasterio
                        Sancti Laurentii. cum <rs key="#Ports">portu</rs> et cursu aquarum. cum <rs
                            key="#Shores">ripis</rs> et omnibus instrumentis eius. et medietatem de
                        uno <rs key="#Mills">molendino</rs>. in predicto fluvio quod <persName><name
                                ref="Iozzelinus">iozzolinus</name></persName> dedit predicto
                        monasterio. similiter cum omnibus instrumentis suis. et <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Burgi #Landed_possessions #Fruits/vegetables #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Privileges #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3020">sancti petri</orgName> sitam ante
                        predictum monasterium Sancti Laurentii. et <rs
                            key="#Burgi #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >Burgum</rs> eiusdem ecclesie qui est situs in <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">ortis</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris</rs> quas <persName><name ref="Hugo Blancus">Hugo
                            blancus</name></persName> dedit eidem monasterio in ea securitate et
                        libertate sicut continetur <rs key="#Privileges">privilegio</rs> quod
                        iordanus princeps pater meus. fecit et concessit prefato monasterio. et <rs
                            key="#Churches">Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Rivers #Landed_possessions #Mills #Coloni/tenants #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3021">Sancti Nicolai</orgName> que est in
                            <placeName ref="#places/695">saone</placeName>. in territorio <placeName
                            ref="#places/2363">calme</placeName>. cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris</rs> et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">hominibus</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Mills">molendinis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Rivers #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">cursibus
                            aquarum</rs> qui sunt in saone et circa saonem. quod <persName
                            ref="#people/3074">Guillelmus de alno</persName> dedit prescripto
                        monasterio cum omnibus suis pertinentiis qualiter monasterium modo possidet
                        et dominatur. et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terras</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Coloni/tenants">homines</rs> et <rs key="#Mills">molendina</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Rivers">cursus aquarum</rs> que sunt in loco <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Rivers #Landed_possessions #Mills #Coloni/tenants"
                            ref="#places/4021">montanarii</placeName> que predictus Guillelmus dedit
                        monasterio cum omnibus suis pertinentiis qualiter monasterium ea modo
                        dominatur. et <rs key="#nephew/nieceOf">Nepotes</rs>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbyteri</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Bernardus">Leonardi</name></persName>
                        cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et omnibus suis pertinentiis
                        qualiter predictus Guillelmus de alno eos tenuit et dominatus est. et
                        prenominato monasterio dedit. et <rs key="#Churches">Ecclesiam</rs><orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3007"> Sancti Andree</orgName> que est in
                            <placeName ref="#places/2363" key="#Villages/settlements"
                            >calmo</placeName> cum suis pertinentiis. et <rs key="#Churches"
                            >Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3009">Sancti Andree </orgName>que est in
                        territorio <placeName key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/571"
                            >suesse</placeName>. cum omnibus que modo possidet et dominatur et que
                        ei pertinent. et <rs key="#Churches">Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3008">Sancte
                            Marie</orgName> et <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3019">Sancti Iohannis</orgName> que sunt in
                        territorio <placeName key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/4009"
                            >miniani</placeName>. quas <persName><name ref="Hugo Sorellus">Ugo
                                sorellus</name></persName> dedit et optulit <rs key="#Hospitals"
                            >ospitali</rs> predicti monasterii cum omnibus ad eas pertinentibus. et
                            <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3010">Sancte Crucis</orgName> quod est in
                        territorio <placeName ref="#places/3483">Caiazie</placeName>. cum omnibus
                        suis pertinentiis. et <rs key="#Casalia">casale</rs> qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Casalia #Coloni/tenants" ref="#places/4006"><geogName
                                key="#Casalia #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants"
                                ref="#estates/3004">marzanum frigidum</geogName></placeName> cum <rs
                            key="#Coloni/tenants">hominibus</rs> et omnibus suis pertinentiis. et
                            <rs key="#Churches">Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3433">Sancti Martini</orgName> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/3444" key="#Villages/settlements">magdalone</placeName>. et
                            <rs key="#Churches">Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3012">Sancte Marie</orgName> de <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/2341">Iuliano</placeName>. cum
                            <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">hominibus</rs> et omnibus suis pertinentiis.
                        et <rs key="#Churches">Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3005">Sancte Marie de spelunca</orgName>. et <rs
                            key="#Churches">Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3013">Sancti Salvatoris</orgName> de <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/4011">vallo</placeName>. et <rs
                            key="#Churches">Ecclesiam</rs>. <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3014">Sancte Marie</orgName> de <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/4013">domicella</placeName>. et
                            <rs key="#Churches">Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3015">Sancti Angeli</orgName> de <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/4012">Lauro</placeName> cum <rs
                            key="#Coloni/tenants">hominibus</rs> et cum omnibus earum pertinentiis
                        et cum <rs key="#Decima">decimatione</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Animals #Decima"
                            ref="#places/4014">Nucerie</placeName> de <rs key="#Cereals"
                        >annona</rs>. et de <rs key="#Wine">vino</rs>. de <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">fructibus</rs> et de <rs key="#Animals"
                            >animalibus</rs>. et <rs key="#Churches">Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3003">Sancti Cononis</orgName>. et <rs
                            key="#Churches">Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3004">Sancti Severini</orgName> que sunt in
                            <placeName key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/4003"
                            >Acerra</placeName>. et <rs key="#Churches">Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3022">Sancti Laurentii</orgName> que est in
                        territorio <placeName ref="#places/4023">Suessole</placeName> et <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/4003">Acerre</placeName>. in
                            <placeName key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/4022"
                            >pantano</placeName> scilicet iusta <rs key="#Forests">boscum</rs>. cum
                        omnibus earum pertinentiis et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terras</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">villanos</rs> quos <persName
                            ref="#people/3031">Rainulfus de Argentia</persName> dedit predicto
                        monasterio in territorio Acerre. et <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            ref="#places/4005">Casollam</placeName>. et <rs key="#Churches"
                            >Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3023">Sancte Marie</orgName> cum <rs
                            key="#Coloni/tenants">villanis</rs> et pertinentiis suis. sicuti
                        predictos patres meos et ego ipse dedimus predicto monasterio. et <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Monasteries"
                            >Sancti Vincentii</orgName> cum <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">hominibus</rs>
                        et omnibus suis pertinentiis et duo <rs
                            key="#Mills #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >molendina</rs> que sunt in <placeName key="#Mills" ref="#places/2865"
                            >Laneo</placeName> ad <placeName ref="#places/4015">pontem
                            silicis</placeName>. et sex <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">villanos</rs> quos
                                <persName><name ref="Unfredus de Calo">Omfridus de
                            Calvo</name></persName> iamdicto monasterio dedit. et unum <rs
                            key="#Mills #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >molendinum</rs> pertinens monasterio quod est ad <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Mills" ref="#places/4016"
                            >Calabrizitum</placeName> in aqua <placeName ref="#places/2865"
                            >Lanei</placeName>. cum omnibus pertinentiis suis et predictis villanis
                        et molendinis pertinentibus et <rs key="#Priests">presbyterum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Marius">marium</name></persName> qui est
                        in <rs key="#Villas">villa</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Villas" ref="#places/4007"><geogName key="#Villas"
                                ref="#estates/3005">Gariliani</geogName></placeName> cum tota
                        familia sua et cum omnibus suis pertinentiis qualiter tenuit <persName><name
                                ref="Richardus fil. Gunduini">Riccardus filius Gunduini
                            </name></persName>qui dedit monasterio. et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            >Ecclesiam</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Coloni/tenants #Churches" ref="#places/4002"
                            >Nobile</placeName> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >terras</rs> et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">villanos</rs> sicut princeps
                        Riccardus dedit monasterio. et <rs key="#Decima">decimationem</rs> de
                            <placeName key="#Villages/settlements #Decima" ref="#places/4017"
                            >Rampale</placeName> quam <persName><name ref="Hugardus de Claromonte"
                                >uhardus de Claromonte</name></persName> dedit monasterio. et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terras</rs> et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants"
                            >villanos</rs> qui sunt in loco <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Landed_possessions #Coloni/tenants"
                            ref="#places/4018">piponis</placeName> sicut <persName><name
                                ref="Raginaldus fil. Hugonis">Raynaldus filius
                            Ugonis</name></persName> dedit monasterio. et <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3001">Sancti blasii</orgName> quod est prope
                        prescriptum monasterium. cum <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">hominibus</rs> et
                        omnibus sibi pertinentibus. et <rs key="#Petiae">startiam</rs> que dicitur
                        de <placeName ref="#places/4019" key="#Petiae"
                            ><geogName>Ceraso</geogName></placeName> quam <rs key="#heirTo"
                            >heredes</rs> Ugonis blanci dederunt monasterio et <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">ortos</rs> et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants"
                            >curtisanos</rs> qui sunt prope muros averse. sicut Ugo blancus dedit
                        monasterio in quibus prefatus burgus situs est. et <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >viridiarium</rs> quod est iuxta <rs key="#Markets">foris</rs> de die
                        sabbati et <rs key="#Lakes">lacum</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Lakes #Fisheries #Fish #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Canals #Fluvial_transport #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#places/701">patriensem</placeName> cum <rs
                            key="#Fluvial_transport">luntribus</rs> et <rs key="#Fisheries #Fish"
                            >paratis et piscationibus</rs> et universis pertinentiis suis sicut
                        pater meus et ego tenui et dominati fuimus et quicquid iure pertinet
                        monasterio antiquitus in <rs key="#Canals">canalibus</rs> et in toto lacu
                        patriensi. et <rs key="#Churches">Ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3024">Sancti
                            Renati</orgName> qui in <rs key="#Vici">vico</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Vici" ref="#places/4024">cupuli</placeName> cum omnibus
