                            >zampicari</placeName> et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">villanos</rs>. et
                            <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terram</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Coloni/tenants" ref="#places/2801"
                            >centora</placeName>. et <rs key="#Churches">Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3025">sancti viti
                        </orgName>que est in loco <placeName ref="#places/4027"
